ing integrity themselves.\", \"from\": 6647, \"to\": 6797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese had 23 swimmers who had tested positive before the Tokyo olympic games, so China has nothing to complain about.\", \"from\": 6799, \"to\": 6918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6799, \"end\": 6806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9997846764714814, \"rank\": 0.000210227444508281, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 6858, \"end\": 6877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.276730817141597e-15, \"text\": \"Tokyo olympic games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 6882, \"end\": 6887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9998662762424226, \"rank\": 6.852075981673668e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They should never have been allowed to compete in the olympics again.\", \"from\": 6919, \"to\": 6988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once you are caught there should be no second chance.\", \"from\": 6989, \"to\": 7042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This goes for US or any other swimmers who are caught and no flaky 'contaminated meat' excuses should be entertained  Sign up to receive free daily think pieces from leading analysts or our weekly digest, that includes our editorial and a collection of recent articles in brief.\", \"from\": 7043, \"to\": 7321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7057, \"end\": 7059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999793776626, \"rank\": 2.062238571286444e-08, \"text\": \"US\